vices/service/ndnp/mohi/batch_mohi_boone_ver01/data/sn89066313/00211109609/1910061701/0552.pdf", "segment_count": 4, "url": "https://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89066313/1910-06-17/ed-1/", "word_coordinates": "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service"}], "segment_id": "/service/ndnp/mohi/batch_mohi_boone_ver01/data/sn89066313/00211109609/1910061701/0552.xml", "segments": [{"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn89066313/1910-06-17/ed-1/?sp=4"], "batch": ["mohi_boone_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "composite_location": ["0/united states/", "1/united states/missouri/", "2/united states/missouri/boone/", "3/united states/missouri/boone/columbia/"], "contributor": ["state historical society of missouri; columbia, mo"], "date": "1910-06-17", "dates": ["1910-06-17"], "description": ["UNIVERSITY MISSOURIAN FRIDAY JUNE 17 1910 PAGE FOUR ASSEMBLY DANGE COLUMBIA HALL Saturday Night June 18 This is the first dance held since the summer students have arrived and they are all invited to attend YOU WILL HAVE NO ANXIETY concerning funds while away from home if you purchase MERCANTILE TRUST CO OR AMERICAN EXPRESS CO Travelers Checks These checks though perfectly protecting you from loss arc the embodiment of simplicity We issue them in denominations of 10 20 50 and 100 They can be cashed anywhere in the world Call and see us for full particulars BOONE COUNTY TRUST CO Lack of Exercise During Vacation Xow that the school year is nearly lit an end the physical exercises which are a part of every city school program are likely to lie ended also much to the loss of many little irls who are bcneiiiin by such instruc tion Of course with freedom from studies and confinement in the school room there comes more general physi cal activity but it is not of the system atic type which has been taught dur ing the school year with the view of developing certain muscles and bring ing into action others infrequently"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "202